
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Aditya Jain — Product Manager</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a08;
    --surface: #111110;
    --surface2: #1a1a17;
    --border: #2a2a26;
    --accent: #c8f04a;
    --accent2: #f04a4a;
    --text: #e8e8e2;
    --muted: #6b6b65;
    --serif: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    --mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    --sans: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* CUSTOM CURSOR */
  .cursor {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, width 0.2s, height 0.2s;
    mix-blend-mode: difference;
  }
  .cursor-ring {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,240,74,0.5);
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1), width 0.25s, height 0.25s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  body:hover .cursor { transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
  body:hover .cursor-ring { transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.4rem 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
  }
  nav.scrolled {
    background: rgba(10,10,8,0.9);
    border-color: var(--border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .nav-links a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; bottom: -3px; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px; background: var(--accent);
    transform: scaleX(0); transition: transform 0.25s;
    transform-origin: left;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .nav-links a:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

  /* HERO */
  #hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
    padding: 0 3rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-noise {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .hero-grid-lines {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 80px 80px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 8rem;
    max-width: 1100px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 8.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 500px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.6s ease forwards;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; align-items: center;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.8s ease forwards;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #0a0a08;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 10px) 0, 100% 10px, 100% 100%, 10px 100%, 0 calc(100% - 10px));
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #e0ff6a; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .btn-secondary {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .btn-secondary .arrow { transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .btn-secondary:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

  .hero-bottom {
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 1s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-scroll-hint {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 40px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .scroll-line::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: -100%;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: var(--accent);
    animation: scrollSlide 2s 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex; gap: 3rem;
  }
  .stat {
    text-align: right;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* MARQUEE */
  .marquee-wrap {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    background: var(--surface);
  }
  .marquee-track {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    animation: marquee 20s linear infinite;
    white-space: nowrap;
    width: max-content;
  }
  .marquee-item {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .marquee-dot {
    width: 5px; height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* SECTION COMMON */
  section { padding: 7rem 3rem; }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }
  .section-label::before {
    content: '';
    width: 2rem; height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  #about { background: var(--surface); }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .about-text p strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }

  .about-right { padding-top: 1rem; }
  .skill-category {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .skill-category:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .skill-cat-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  .skill-tags {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .tag:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(200,240,74,0.05);
  }
  .tag.accent {
    background: rgba(200,240,74,0.1);
    border-color: rgba(200,240,74,0.3);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* PORTFOLIO */
  #portfolio { background: var(--bg); }
  .portfolio-header {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .view-all {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .view-all:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  .portfolio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5px;
    background: var(--border);
  }
  .portfolio-item {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    min-height: 320px;
  }
  .portfolio-item:hover { background: var(--surface); }
  .portfolio-item::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 3px; height: 0;
    background: var(--accent);
    transition: height 0.4s ease;
  }
  .portfolio-item:hover::after { height: 100%; }
  .portfolio-item.featured {
    grid-column: span 2;
    min-height: 280px;
  }

  .portfolio-num {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .portfolio-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .portfolio-item.featured .portfolio-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
  .portfolio-desc {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .portfolio-meta {
    display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .meta-tag {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .portfolio-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 3rem; right: 3rem;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .portfolio-item:hover .portfolio-arrow {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .portfolio-impact {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .impact-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* BLOG */
  #blog { background: var(--surface); }
  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5px;
    background: var(--border);
  }
  .blog-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .blog-card:hover { background: var(--surface2); }
  .blog-card.featured { grid-row: span 2; }

  .blog-date {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .blog-category {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,240,74,0.3);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .blog-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .blog-card.featured .blog-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
  .blog-excerpt {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .blog-read {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: auto;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .blog-card:hover .blog-read { color: var(--accent); }

  /* CONTACT */
  #contact {
    background: var(--bg);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .contact-left .section-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem); }

  .contact-tagline {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-email {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
    transition: gap 0.2s;
  }
  .contact-email:hover { gap: 1.2rem; }

  .contact-right {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 3.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

  .form-field {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .form-field label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .form-field input,
  .form-field textarea {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    resize: none;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .form-field input:focus,
  .form-field textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .form-field textarea { min-height: 100px; }

  .form-submit {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--bg);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 8px) 0, 100% 8px, 100% 100%, 8px 100%, 0 calc(100% - 8px));
  }
  .form-submit:hover { background: #e0ff6a; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .footer-copy {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .footer-socials { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .footer-socials a {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .footer-socials a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes scrollSlide {
    0% { left: -100%; }
    100% { left: 100%; }
  }
  @keyframes marquee {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  /* SCROLL REVEAL */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
  .reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="navbar">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Aditya Jain</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#portfolio">Work</a></li>
    <li><a href="#blog">Writing</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-noise"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid-lines"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Product Manager · Bengaluru, India</div>
    <h1 class="hero-name">
      I build products
      <em>people love.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Bridging the gap between business goals and user needs — through research, strategy, and a relentless obsession with clarity.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#portfolio" class="btn-primary">View My Work</a>
      <a href="#blog" class="btn-secondary">Read My Thinking <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-bottom">
    <div class="hero-scroll-hint">
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
      Scroll to explore
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">6+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">12</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Products Shipped</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">3M+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Users Impacted</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MARQUEE -->
<div class="marquee-wrap">
  <div class="marquee-track">
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Product Strategy</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>User Research</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Roadmap Planning</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Cross-functional Leadership</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Data-Driven Decisions</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>Agile / Scrum</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span class="marquee-dot"></span>OKR Framework</div>
